'''22 Northmoor Road''' was the home of the Tolkien family for four years, from [[7 January]] [[1926]] to [[14 January]] [[1930]], until they "decided to move in over the fence" according to [[John Tolkien|John]] and [[Priscilla Tolkien]] in [[The Tolkien Family Album]].<ref name=CG>{{CG|C}}, p. 135,152</ref>
